<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c2">(٠٠٠ - ٥٦٤ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">(٠٠٠ - ١١٦٩ م)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
